title: Super Stitches Crochet: Essential Techniques Plus a Dictionary o
description: General Adult. Designed with a user-friendly, lay-flat binding, a comprehensive, illustrated resource offers a thorough introduction to the art of crochet, with detailed instruction in a variety of useful techniques, a dictionary of more than 180 stitches and patterns, and helpful tips on selecting yarns, choosing hooks, understanding abbreviations and symbols in crochet patterns, and more. Original.
